{"tid":1806723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"共狗戰略：腰斬和理非遊行、分化民陣、報細人數","createTime":"2020-01-01T12:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T13:48:48.000Z","uid":90601,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97dba65240cf4561aba098b3f54e33a4793f0286","tid":1806723,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"今日唔止出重狗 直頭網軍盡出 唔關事既post都會見到有人屌民陣<br />\n可見西環見勇武拉唔曬<br />\n2020最大目標會將會係和理非<br />\n今日見到起碼過5/60萬就即刻搞事腰斬<br />\n目的就係唔想和理非覺得自己既行動有用<br />\n想令你地覺得遊行無用 人數唔夠多 民陣廢物<br />\n慢慢用「削兵之計」去令和理非有更少行動<br />\n目標相信係減少黃色經濟圈既行動力<br />\n同埋要硬保2020立法會大選<br />\n<br />\n今日有到現場既都知其實比想像中多人<br />\n唔好俾黑警同西環拋到<br />\n同時要小心被帶風向 中共一定會出力分化和勇"},{"pid":"fe4f79524ca29af0d34a57e3fae4ef77cc6da5d4","tid":1806723,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e21249a9de4f89d94a32fecc54dac3b7eb07d50","tid":1806723,"uid":42548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"係喎, 一見多人立刻腰斬, 唔好比人知個實數<br />\n<br />\n好似大陸天災佢地報細數怕中央屌"},{"pid":"b2ae427ab4350f3c838049255559ec368a8c7b77","tid":1806723,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c2bc36cc29808427e0aacdad05e6d2ba6cc95b","tid":1806723,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e21249a9de4f89d94a32fecc54dac3b7eb07d50","tid":1806723,"uid":42548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"係喎, 一見多人立刻腰斬, 唔好比人知個實數<br />\n<br />\n好似大陸天災佢地報細數怕中央屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"岩岩民陣出左聲明 預計如果無腰斬會過103萬"},{"pid":"002e2b5c94158594d435f76e907f9f0dff59a6aa","tid":1806723,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:55: